Katrina Amy Alexandra Alexis Price, previously known by the pseudonym Jordan, is an English media personality, model, businesswoman, singer and author.
Price rose to prominence in 1996 for her glamour modeling work with appearances, billed as "Jordan", on Page 3 in British tabloids The Sun and The Daily Star.
